Read `PROJECT_CONSTITUTION.md` before making changes.

- Build incrementally; one phase at a time.
- Business logic belongs in `services/`, not UI components.
- AI calls go through `lib/ai.ts` and `lib/gemini.ts`.
- Prompts live in `prompts/` only.
- Validate external input with Zod.
- First consumer project: Pakistan Disaster Response AI Command Center.
